<p>Установить новый адрес:</p>








  <div class="shortcode shortcode-codeblock shortcode-codeblock-sh">
    <div class="d-flex mb-3 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="flex-grow-1 rounded overflow-hidden" id="clipboard-ef509fc16b99e2980d5c0479c89b9b69"><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"><span class="line"><span class="cl">git remote set-url origin <span class="s1">&#39;[URL]&#39;</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
